10:
We are the chosen proxy—those
who have been entrusted with their
will.
15:
Here and now we shall prevail
against our subjugators. We will
crush the stars, and shatter the
night.
32:
Are you KIDDING me?! You had
something like THAT hidden up your
sleeves this whole time?
34:
Haha... Hahahaha! Isn't it a sight to
behold? This is the Titan that shall
shatter the stars!
35:
With the power of a god at our side,
even the kingdom stands no
chance against us—
52:
This is insane... Forget the kingdom...
The whole world's in trouble!
62: Of course I find you instead!
69:
Did you and yours summon that
gigantic monster? Answer me!
73: What the hell is that thing?!
76:
Rashid and his comrades called it a
Titan.
84:
How gullible do you think I am?
There's no way an actual god exists...
89:
Listen, I'm just telling you what they
said! They only summoned it
because you pushed them into a
corner!
92:
So now what? You want that
powerful monster for yourself too?
96:
Well, do whatever you want. I'm
gonna put a stop to this.
101:
I swung my bloodied blade again
and again, believing that I was
doing it for the good of the
borderlands... But if this is the result
of that...
118:
Found you faster than I expected,
thanks to these hunks of junk!
122:
Oh! Glad to see you made it out
okay, Nimbus!
126:
After all the fighting we've been
through...
